#!/usr/bin/env bash
# AI generated weekly report

claude --allowedTools 'Bash(git:*) Bash(gh:*)' -p '
Generate a report of my work from last week by:

1. Searching my GitHub pull requests for PRs merged last Monday through Friday
2. Organizing the report with:
   - List of PRs, grouped by project (one of Treasury, Ramp Inpsect, Buildkite, Testing, Other)
   - Lines of code added and removed for each PR (e.g. +1000 -500)

Format as markdown
' | glow -
